{"tid":2083720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國過百萬人聯署修改美國國旗","createTime":"2020-06-29T02:52:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T02:00:07.000Z","uid":109780,"like":348,"dislike":121,"uniUserReply":108,"replies":[{"pid":"e89f561d73039914073932bcc7aa0153b3825fd8","tid":2083720,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T02:52:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O9DwWxM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO9DwWxM.jpg&h=8428f027&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/the-white-house-changing-the-american-flag-and-national-anthem?utm_source=share_petition&amp;utm_medium=custom_url&amp;recruited_by_id=b850be70-b71f-11ea-8cf3-e94b44f379e7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fthe-white-house-changing-the-american-flag-and-national-anthem%3Futm_source%3Dshare_petition%26utm_medium%3Dcustom_url%26recruited_by_id%3Db850be70-b71f-11ea-8cf3-e94b44f379e7&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8Y6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=3a488185\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/the-white-house-changing-the-american-flag-and-national-anthem?utm_source=share_petition&amp;utm_medium=custom_url&amp;recruited_by_id=b850be70-b71f-11ea-8cf3-e94b44f379e7</a><br />\n<br />\n為聲援&ldquo;黑人的命也是命&rdquo;運動，國旗左上角原本藍色的底色被修改成黑色﹔而象徵50個州的白色星星則被改為卡通人物Manny Helffley，該形象來自美國喜劇作品《小屁孩日記》，請願發起人稱，Manny Helffley代表了團結、正義、不惹麻煩﹔星條旗的紅色橫條被改成黃色，因為黃色象徵喜悅、樂觀、智慧、正能量等等。<br />\n<br />\n又黃又黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />手足嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99565fc887a82f6ec17fc25b75ec1cc29660cc0f","tid":2083720,"uid":114487,"like":47,"dislike":2,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T02:52:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qEpj5kb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqEpj5kb.jpg&h=d6